@startuml
title Сетевая схема размещения Telegram-бота для Qmatic Orchestra 6
!include style.iuml
left to right direction
skinparam nodesep 80
skinparam ranksep 90

actor "Посетитель\nTelegram-клиент" as Visitor

cloud "Интернет" as Internet {
  component "Telegram Bot API\napi.telegram.org:443" as TelegramApi <<external>>
}

node "Корпоративный / филиальный контур\nprivate LAN / DC / VPC" as Corp {
  rectangle "APP zone" as AppZone {
    component "Queue Telegram Bot\nPython container / VM\nбез входящего порта" as Bot <<bot>>
  }

  rectangle "SERVICE zone" as ServiceZone {
    component "Qmatic Orchestra 6\nREST API" as RestApi <<orchestra>>
    component "Qmatic Orchestra 6\nCometD / Bayeux" as CometD <<orchestra>>
  }

  rectangle "DATA zone" as DataZone {
    database "Orchestra DB\nзакрыта от Интернета" as Db
  }

  rectangle "Infra / Ops" as OpsZone {
    component "DNS" as Dns
    component "NTP" as Ntp
    component "Log collector\nstdout / journald / ELK" as Logs
  }
}

Visitor --> TelegramApi : 1. сообщения боту
Bot --> TelegramApi : 2. HTTPS 443 outbound\ngetUpdates / sendMessage
Bot --> RestApi : 3. REST outbound\nGET services / POST visits
Bot --> CometD : 4. CometD outbound\nhandshake / subscribe / connect
RestApi --> Db : 5. read/write visits, services
CometD --> Db : 6. publish VISIT_CALL context
Bot --> Dns : 7. DNS lookup
Bot --> Ntp : 8. time sync
Bot --> Logs : 9. application logs

Internet -[#DC2626,dashed]-> Bot : DENY ingress
Internet -[#DC2626,dashed]-> RestApi : DENY public access
Internet -[#DC2626,dashed]-> Db : DENY public DB access

legend bottom center
|= № |= Разрешённый поток |= Назначение |
| 1 | Visitor -> Telegram Bot API | пользовательские команды и callbacks |
| 2 | Bot -> Telegram API: TCP/443 | polling + отправка сообщений |
| 3 | Bot -> Orchestra REST | получение услуг и создание визита |
| 4 | Bot -> Orchestra CometD | подписка на VISIT_CALL по prefix филиала |
| 5-6 | Orchestra -> DB | чтение/запись бизнес-данных и событий |
| 7-9 | Bot -> DNS/NTP/Logs | инфраструктурные исходящие подключения |
--
Входящий порт из Интернета для бота не нужен: используется polling, не webhook.
endlegend
@enduml
